{"tid":591644,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"開瓦斯輕生卻點菸？45間房子遭波及　鄰居送醫他卻沒事…","createTime":"2018-03-13T17:23:04.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-14T05:23:49.000Z","uid":87540,"like":14,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"e67562c5e3a66850a06dd27459ec00db451bbb11","tid":591644,"uid":87540,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-13T17:23:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20180309/640_12ec14a2f4b6705a5a78eb275f0cb28e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20180309%2F640_12ec14a2f4b6705a5a78eb275f0cb28e.jpg&h=4e684e21&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n男開瓦斯吞安眠藥想自殺　睡醒忘記點菸引起大爆炸。翻攝自《IBC岩手放送》<br />\n<br />\n男子在住家開瓦斯吞安眠藥想自殺，睡醒忘記有開瓦斯，點火抽菸引起大爆炸，男子沒事反而造成鄰居受傷、周圍住家外牆、窗戶等受損，遭到警方逮捕。<br />\n<br />\n據《IBC岩手放送》報導，日本盛岡市32歲男子栗原義明，於3月3日早上11點多，在家裡開瓦斯後使用打火機引起爆炸，造成兩位70多歲的鄰居受傷。栗原義明的律師辯稱，栗原會開瓦斯讓房內充滿氣體的原因，是他想要藉此自殺，並吞安眠藥想在睡夢中逝去，但是醒來後忘記有開瓦斯，結果起床點火抽菸引起大爆炸，「栗原沒有想要引起爆炸的意圖」。<br />\n<br />\n警方日前將栗原逮捕後，栗原表示「對周圍的鄰居造成困擾，真的相當抱歉」。這起爆炸造成半徑170公尺範圍內的房子損害，住戶也完全無法接受栗原的說法，警方將對栗原為何要開瓦斯等行動，做詳細調查。（即時新聞中心／綜合報導）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20180309/640_f44a79246c8de73588f02ff580664f0b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20180309%2F640_f44a79246c8de73588f02ff580664f0b.jpg&h=4a7a3c35&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n翻攝自《IBC岩手放送》<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20180309/640_c7752dcb93996f2d850bb43fae41ac2a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20180309%2F640_c7752dcb93996f2d850bb43fae41ac2a.jpg&h=1dfb878b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n翻攝自《IBC岩手放送》<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20180309/640_0c69995c33b60b0f30a4a0226a3a98ef.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20180309%2F640_0c69995c33b60b0f30a4a0226a3a98ef.jpg&h=b0b996f5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n翻攝自日視NEWS24<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20180309/640_88bb8919a9fcbf783203037721787e56.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20180309%2F640_88bb8919a9fcbf783203037721787e56.jpg&h=f0e92a66&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n翻攝自日視NEWS24<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.appledaily.com/new/realtime/20180309/1311576/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fnew%2Frealtime%2F20180309%2F1311576%2F&d=AuF%2BR4E1NNtI17gjFGCCJ57TfgnX9jywtYe9GXZmhCU%3D&h=27fb7b77\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fnew%2Frealtime%2F20180309%2F1311576%2F&h=e2ea860d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://tw.appledaily.com/new/realtime/20180309/1311576/</a>"},{"pid":"c1030c87b4c899eea9e6abcebc52e5ed988d305a","tid":591644,"uid":116530,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-13T17:25:33.000Z","msg":"點解自己間屋爆炸會冇事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9b0158e6fde85e7fa4f12ef0d2c37325d1f3df5c","tid":591644,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-13T17:25:45.000Z","msg":"居然咁都無人死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"25f8500b573f918992da34204f128878c7d72594","tid":591644,"uid":161709,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-13T17:30:37.000Z","msg":"鄰居好慘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a10d0d94110266de07feb4117fac819a58117b25","tid":591644,"uid":39698,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-13T17:44:05.000Z","msg":"最危險既地方就最安全原來係真<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3ae327caaaad41cb82f9d721039939f098f93080","tid":591644,"uid":45232,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedB